{
  "chapter": 84,
  "chapter_summary": "苏樱用假药戏弄江玉郎，谎称其病入膏肓后喂下致病药丸，再以剖腹取药相威胁，最终将江玉郎通过机关床弹入地洞。随后苏樱来到关押小鱼儿的山洞，两人隔着铁栅门斗嘴调情。小鱼儿回忆闯入天外天与魏无牙斗智斗力的经过：他故意不坐机关椅子，识破魏无牙的十八道机关，最终故意挨一刀中毒飞刀以脱离战斗。苏樱透露魏无牙二十年前被移花宫主击败后闭门苦练，小鱼儿则提及花无缺是移花宫主唯一的男弟子，并感叹本可与花无缺做朋友却不得不成为仇人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "只因有病的吃了这药，病势立刻加重十倍，没有病的吃了这药，也立刻百病俱生，而且全身都疼得要命……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘……在下与姑娘无冤无仇，姑娘为何要如此害我？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你不是说已病入膏肓了么？我不愿将你当成个专门说谎的无耻之徒，所以好心给你吃下这药，你真的生了病，就不算说谎了……而且，我还怕你病得太慢，所以又好心替你揉肚子，助药力发散。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你看，我对你这么好，你还不谢谢我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "苏姑娘……苏前辈，我……小人现在才知道你的厉害了，求求你瞧在白山君夫妻的面上，饶了我吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "哎哟，我倒忘了你是白山君夫妇的朋友。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑……姑娘千万忘不得的。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不错，你既是他们的朋友，我就不能眼见你病死在这里了，我好歹也得救救你……只可惜这药并非毒药，所以也没有解药，你又吃了下去……这怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "求求姑娘，姑娘一定有法子的。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "有了！我想起个法子来了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我只有剖开你肚子，将那药丸拿出来。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "剖开我肚子？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但你放心，我一定会轻轻的割，轻轻地将那药丸拿出来，你一定连丝毫痛苦都没有。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "肚子剖开，人已死了，还会觉得疼么？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你真是个聪明人。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这就是我们家祖传的止疼秘方，手疼割手，脚疼割脚，头疼切脑袋，肚疼剖肚子，担保你着手成春，药到'命'除。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刀呢……刀呢……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘……姑娘千万莫要……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你不要我替你治病了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "不要了，不要了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你既不要，我也没法子，但这可是你自已的主意，不能怪我不救你，对不对？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "对对对，对极了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "现在你可知道，谁是天下第一个大傻蛋么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "是我，我就是天下第一个大傻蛋，大混帐，大……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "没出息，这么大个男人还哭，真叫我见了难受……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个哭，一个笑，这两人倒是天生一对，就让你们去作作伴吧……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_unknown_man",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "一个人喝酒没意思，姓苏的丫头，你还不过来陪陪我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_unknown_man",
      "text": "他才真是我命中的魔星，我为什么看见他就没了主意……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_unknown_man",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姓苏的丫头，你还不来？我就……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我这不是来了么？也没见过你这么性急的人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你嫌我性子火急了么？我天生就是这样的脾气，你看不惯最好就不要看。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但我若不想你，又怎会急着要你来？别人常说，一日不见，如隔三秋，但我简直片刻也不能不见你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我知道我这条命，迟早总是要被你气死的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "干万死不得，你死了，还有谁来陪我喝酒。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你既然要我来陪你喝酒，为什么不把酒杯拿来？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你既然要来陪我喝酒，为什么不进来？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我在外面陪你喝，还不是一样么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "那怎么会一样？你一定得坐在我旁边，陪我说话，我的酒才喝得下去，我方才不是说过，我有多么想你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "反正我在外面，你一样还是能看得到我的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你这臭丫头，死丫头，谁要你来陪我喝酒，你快滚吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "反正你拍我马屁，我也不进去，你骂我，我还是不进去的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你为何不进来？难道怕我吃了你？我又不是李大嘴。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我知道你不吃人，但我一开门进去，你就要乘机冲出来了，是么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你又不是我肚子里的蛔虫，怎知道我的心意？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我知道你是个好人，而且对我很好，我骂你，你也不生气，但你为什么偏偏要将我关在这里呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你是个爱动的人，性子又急，我若不将你关起来，你一定早就走了，但你的伤却到现在还没有好，若是一走动，就更糟了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "原来你还是一番好意。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但你这番好意，我却不领情。我是死是活，都不关你的事，你莫以为你救了我，我就该听你的话，感激你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我……我并没有要你感激我，是么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "说老实话，你为什么要救我，我可真有些弄不清。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那天，我恰巧到'天外天'去……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "什么'天外天'，那里只不过是个老鼠洞而已！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，就算是老鼠洞，你也不必生气呀！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我为何不生气？现在我一听'老鼠'两个字就头疼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但这两字是你自己说的，我并没有说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我听人说都头疼，自己说自然头更疼了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不会不说么，又没有人强迫你说。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我不说又嘴痒，我……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你为何还不说下去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那天我到那地方去，本是去拿要他们替我刨的药草，准知却见到了你，你恰巧也到了那里。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我会到那鬼地方去，算我倒霉，你遇见我，也算你倒霉。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但那天我看见你的时候，你却连一点倒霉的样子都没有，你身上穿的衣服虽然破破烂烂，但那神气却像是穿着世上最华贵、最好看的衣服。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "还有呢？我不但很神气，长得也不难看呀！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，你长得的确不难看，尤其是你的眼睛……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我的眉毛、我的鼻子、我的嘴难道就不好看么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你从头到脚，没有一个地方不好看……这够了么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "嗯……这还差不多……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我本不是个很容易吃惊的人，但我见到你时，我……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你见到我时，眼睛都直了，嘴也张大了，活像瞧见了大头鬼似的，那时我真想在你嘴里塞个大鸡蛋。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那只因我心里实在奇怪。你怎会找到……找到那地方的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "那其中自然有个缘故，但你……你却不必知道，因为无论我是怎会找到那鬼地方的，都不关你的事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "还有令我奇怪的是，你到了那里，竟一点也不害怕。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "那有什么好害怕的？比那地方更恐怖、更骇人的地方，我都见得多了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你见过比……比魏无牙更可怕的人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我从七八岁的时候开始，差不多每隔两三天就要见他一面，但直到现在为止，我一见他的面，还是好像要发抖。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我不是怕他，我只是觉得恶心。他那张脸、那副模样看来简直不是人……他看来简直就像是老天用一只老鼠、一只狐狸、一只狼斩碎了，再用一瓶毒药、一碗臭水揉在一起造成的活鬼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这张嘴可真缺德，但你实在也将他形容得再妙也没有了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "老实说，我见到你们时，心里真觉得有些好笑，你们俩人坐在一起，看来就像香酥鸽子旁摆着堆臭狗屎，世上再也找不出比这更不相配的事了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他虽然不是个好人，但对我……对我却一直很好。这十年来，他简直没有拂过我的心意，我无论要做什么，他全都答应。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "哼，丑八怪拍小美人的马屁，那本就是天经地义的事。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他看见你忽然闯来，而且还有胆子瞪着眼睛向他穷吼，他实在也骇了一跳。这么多年来，我还没见过有人能令他脸上变了颜色的，但他瞧见你时，却连眼睛都好像发绿了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "他只怕本以为洞口的那些破铜烂铁能够拦得住我的，谁知那些东西在我眼里，简直就像是小孩子玩的把戏。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他就是因为你能闯过他布下的十八道机关消息，所以才对你有些顾忌，所以你虽然对他穷吼，他还是坐着不动……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "他既然已知道我的厉害，为何还要令那些蠢才来送死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他自己不动手，却要他门下弟子去动手，为的只是想先试出你的武功来，他也明知那些人不会是你的对手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你以为我不知道他的心意？我是故意不让他瞧出我的武功路数来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "魏无牙实也未想到连他都瞧不出你的武功家数来。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "所以他就一直坐着不出手，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "他就能眼瞧着那些人被我活活打死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那些人虽也是他的门徒弟子，但却都还未能登堂入室，并非他心爱的那几个。何况，别人的死活，他根本就不放在心上，只要对他自己有利，就算要他将他儿子的脑袋切下来送人，他也不会皱一皱眉头的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我早就知道这家伙不是人，谁知他竟连畜牲都不如。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "谁知后来你还是上了他的当了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你懂得什么，若论斗智，就凭他还差得远哩！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但是你……你还是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "斗智他虽斗不过我，斗力我可就斗不过他了。不瞒你说，我实未想到这畜牲的武功，竟有那么厉害！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "据说在二十年前，他武功已可算是天下有数的几个高手之一，'十二星相'能横行江湖，可说全靠他一人之力。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "他这倒不是吹牛，'十二星相'中的人，我也见过两个，武功比起他来，简直连他一成都赶不上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "二十年前，他本以为可以无敌于天下，后来遇着了'移花宫主'，大概是吃了个大亏，所以才闭门洗手，躲到这里来。这二十年他日日夜夜的苦练武功，据他说，现在就算移花宫主姐妹两个一起来，他也未必怕她们了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "他这就是吹牛了，莫说移花宫主自己来，就算移花宫主的徒弟来了，也管叫他吃不了，兜着走。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "移花宫主有几个徒弟？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "女的我不知道，男的却只有一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你和他是朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "本来是可以和他交朋友的，但现在……现在却好像非和他做仇人不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "很好，好极了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "好什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我也知道他要我坐下，本来是想以诡计害我的，我只怕和他斗力，不怕和他斗智，所以也就立刻坐了下来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他那张椅子上，本有机关，只要他的手一按，坐在椅子上的人就要掉下刀坑去，纵然武功再强，只怕也活不成了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "真有这般厉害？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他不但武功颇高，旁门杂学更是样样精通，他以为只要发动机关，你必死无疑，所以才不愿费力和你动手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "他自己只怕也想不到他发动机关之后，我还是好好的坐着未动。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那时不但他奇怪，我也奇怪极了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "老实告诉你，我早已看出那张椅子有古怪了，所以我看来好像已坐下，其实我的屁股根本就没挨着椅子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你真是个鬼灵精。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我借此骂了他两句，谁知道这老畜牲竟比我还沉不住气，竟跳起来就和我动手，我一见他出手，就知道要糟了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你还是和他拼了好一阵，那一场大战，我简直从来也没有见过。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这老畜生倒的确有两下子，不但武功高，招式狠，而且出手又贼又滑，我就算武功比他高，也占不了他的便宜。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他自己也这么样说，就算武功比他高的人，也未必能胜得了他．只因他无论使出什么招式，自己先立于不败之地。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "就因为他出力还是先留三分余力，所以我才能和他支持那么久。但我心里也知道，只要我稍一不慎，就得死在他手里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他手下的确从来没有活口。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我既然知道迟早总要遭他的毒手，连逃也逃不了，心里就在打主意了，我就算要死，也不愿死在这种人手里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "所以你就……你……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "所以我就一步步向后退，退到墙角。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那墙角也有个机关，只要你踩到那里，立刻会有飞刀射出，",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你以为我不知道么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你知道？你知道为何还要去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我就因为已瞧出墙角有机关，就因为已瞧出他要将我诱到那里去，所以才故意好像被他逼得无路可退，一脚踩上那机关，等飞刀射出来时，我也故意装成无法闪避的模样去挨那一刀。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "为什么？你为什么故意要上这个当？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "只因为我不愿死在他手上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你可知道，那飞刀上也有剧毒？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "飞刀上就算有毒，也比他那双鬼爪子好多了，我若被他那鬼爪子抓中，必死无疑，所以我才宁可去挨一刀。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我算准他见我挨了一刀后，就不会再动手了，否则我只有和他打到死为止……现在你总该知道，我并不是真的上了他的当吧？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "若论应变时智计之灵巧，手段之奇秘，心眼儿动得之快，世上只怕真没有几个人比得上你。",
      "tone": "佩服",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你难道还不晓得我是天下第一个聪明人么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 84,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    }
